    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it feels like everything is just... pointless. you look at the news and the climate data and you just realize we're all just living on a countdown. like what is the point in even trying to build a life or make plans when the world is literally falling apart? it just feels like we're all just waiting for the end.",
